# Technical Stack
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.mdc](001-project-overview.mdc)

## Backend Core
- **Language:** Java 21
- **Framework:** Spring Boot 4.0.1
- **Build Tool:** Gradle (latest stable)
- **Architecture:** Layered Architecture (Controller -> Service -> Repository)

## Database & Storage
- **Primary DB:** MySQL 8.x (InnoDB, utf8mb4)
- **Persistence:** JPA / Hibernate
- **Migrations:** Flyway or Liquibase (Recommended)

## API Interface
- **Style:** RESTful API
- **Documentation:** Swagger / OpenAPI 3.0
- **Format:** JSON

## Testing
- **Unit Testing:** JUnit 5, Mockito
- **Integration Testing:** Spring Boot Test, TestContainers (for DB)
- **API Testing:** REST Assured (optional)

## Deployment (Target)
- **Container:** Docker
- **CI/CD:** GitHub Actions (Future)

